{"tid":783602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［勵志］成功需姐夫幹/家姐被幹","createTime":"2018-08-17T15:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T16:49:24.000Z","uid":152224,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"192b96fb290de15a76257fa7f12d6fa9a8289345","tid":783602,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:58:56.000Z","msg":"話說我老豆老母好窮, 月入一萬(老母仲做家庭主婦）<br />\n生咗五件, 仲要迫喺間600呎公屋<br />\n窮人生仔正仆街, 仲要咁多件<br />\n而且爺爺嫲嫲仲要同我地住<br />\n一家九口二十年來都挨窮到仆街<br />\n<br />\n好彩我d家姐都生(保養)得幾好,名牌大學畢業<br />\n現任男朋友全部都係極品筍盤<br />\n分別為: 律師樓老闆,大學教授,投資銀行家, 醫生<br />\n<br />\n而我呢個垃圾細佬一直一事無成, 渾渾噩噩<br />\n二十歲A0, 讀水泡科, 仲未有明確career path<br />\n但我對未來充滿憧憬嘅<br />\n<br />\n利申: 有3間物業, 仲有1間比咗老豆老母"},{"pid":"6d277574040f9d487eb131320fa419a312119c3a","tid":783602,"uid":138252,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"你家姐同時有五個男朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c245bed15943f017d5ee0f106d246742790777e8","tid":783602,"uid":100904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"住公屋又有三間物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ba714dc2ff303f05a1c6472fb14377008b4d32","tid":783602,"uid":152224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d277574040f9d487eb131320fa419a312119c3a","tid":783602,"uid":138252,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"你家姐同時有五個男朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"四個家姐"},{"pid":"bca70b2839f337d22cce0dac5e29e0ee6b1d8ad5","tid":783602,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c245bed15943f017d5ee0f106d246742790777e8","tid":783602,"uid":100904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"住公屋又有三間物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-1